{"tid":1778111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地真係唔可以當被補既手足係condom","createTime":"2019-12-10T16:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T01:37:35.000Z","uid":305579,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f587ff77406b44a3f38c59a4eac92230d8fab7f0","tid":1778111,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"6月至今已經有好多手足被檢控，由輕既非法集結，到重既暴動罪，都足以令手足判入獄，有好多case暫時都只係過左堂，未真正判，但係一旦有第一單個案判左就會成為先例，比其他官借鑒，如果好彩既判罪名不成立，就會救到好多手足，和理非亦都唔會再驚出黎<br />\n所以小弟求下大家，無論黑警點樣放軟手腳，政府點樣叫我地袋住先，我地都一定<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以忘記被捕既手足</span></span><br />\n最後<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"2f47cd6d2d3c192ca2eeda4be5f0d4bdeb0fe0d2","tid":1778111,"uid":18648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:33:58.000Z","msg":"義士唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74d796c175522518988f74c512f258c26623f6d","tid":1778111,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f47cd6d2d3c192ca2eeda4be5f0d4bdeb0fe0d2","tid":1778111,"uid":18648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:33:58.000Z","msg":"義士唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:34:26.000Z","msg":"幫推 p牌推唔到"},{"pid":"fb92a2f84d2989182c534f77a2e595958bedb25b","tid":1778111,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"無忘記過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a927ddd798827cc931d253933496d19c1b449a5","tid":1778111,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe92c30dc41d4e6645246e5d07458dde3602687","tid":1778111,"uid":305579,"like":0,"